{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS","iPadOS","Mac Catalyst"],"tokens":[{"text":"@property","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" (","kind":"text"},{"text":"nonatomic","kind":"keyword"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"readonly","kind":"keyword"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:@S@CLLocationCoordinate2D","text":"CLLocationCoordinate2D","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"coordinate","kind":"identifier"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"languages":["occ"]}]}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation\/coordinate"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation"]]},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation\/coordinate"},"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"title":"coordinate","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"coordinate"}],"symbolKind":"property","externalID":"c:objc(pl)MLNAnnotation(py)coordinate","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"coordinate","kind":"identifier"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Property","role":"symbol"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The center point (specified as a map coordinate) of the annotation. (required)"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"(read-only)"}],"sections":[],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","abstract":[{"text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling.","type":"text"}],"type":"topic","title":"MapLibre","role":"collection"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation/coordinate":{"fragments":[{"text":"coordinate","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation\/coordinate","kind":"symbol","title":"coordinate","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation\/coordinate","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The center point (specified as a map coordinate) of the annotation. (required)"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"(read-only)"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation":{"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNAnnotation"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","title":"MLNAnnotation","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" protocol is used to provide annotation-related information"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to a map view. To use this protocol, you adopt it in any custom objects that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"store or represent annotation data. Each object then serves as the source of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"information about a single map annotation and provides critical information,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"such as the annotation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"objects to handle the display."}]}}}